  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I thought-- then that night, when I'd been to work at night, I knew it-- I looked at my parents-- I knew this was the  last time I'm gonna see them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I know we working, they'll keep us for awhile.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they would be sent away right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew what they were doing with the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the time, it's been a few years after-- in the war going in, and we knew exactly what's happening to the people, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One thing what happened-- you know, I told you when we were in the factory after they liquidated Jewish people, and then we didn't have no place to stay in the factory so they-- they took us back to the city where we used to live in like a little ghetto from the workers.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came-- there was a lot of people still, you know, from-- so they told us that my father-- they saw my father and mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were hidden for a few days, but they couldn't exist without eating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- so they had to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we came in the-- in the city from the factory, we had to stay in that little town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- somebody told us they saw them sending them away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So just a few hours before we went to the [? market-- ?] to the-- to the place where we-- they let us live there from the factory, so we found out that they sent them away.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Older brothers were sent right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The older ones.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- I don't think the same transport, because I told you my parents were hidden with-- a few days and then they came out.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
